    <item>
      <title>深度冻结推动美国最大电网电力需求创冬季新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/deep-freeze-propels-power-demand-on-largest-us-grid-to-winter-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国南部地区摆脱 130 年来最严重的暴风雪，严寒天气导致美国东部的电力供应紧张，该国最大电网的用电需求达到冬季历史最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/deep-freeze-propels-power-demand-on-largest-us-grid-to-winter-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 13:50:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
